  "lyrics": "I see you lookin' good by the way you walk I see you lookin' so good, makes your light shine I've been givin' you a golden hue It won't take me long, girl Just have a little drink this year Won't take me long, girl You can tell me yes or no quite quickly Has anybody ever told you you're Like a magnet that makes me fall forward No matter if I wanna repeat past mistakes You're the thing that makes me do better But it won't take me long To tell you all the ways you help me know Won't take me long For me to show you just all the ways you could complete me But we can wait a little second left, not a little second right We're not here to fight, no I know I just talked to you now we just met But maybe you deserve a second round It's not gonna take me long With your heart singin' that song It's not gonna take me long When we're combustin' in the sheets Yeah, I feel so free, I'm flyin' now Thank you for all the days when it Oh, girl, it won't take me long To imagine a future long with happiness It won't take me long Till you've got me inside of you Like my love for kindness Like my shining lining Like the silver that binds us all together Gray matter from the heart is like a red tether And it's not gonna take me long It's not gonna take me long at all To love you like you've never been in love before, baby All this emotional stunt I'm runnin' to you Now I can see that we're right together Even if we just met, imagine that Imagine all this in the span of this total second So just think of what a lover I could be And just think about a better season You'll see that's the line We're gonna pass dead right here all night Oh, baby, it won't take me long To love every second that I'm around you It won't take me long Cause you're dynamite and I'm so glad I met you These eyes are cryin' These eyes have seen a lot of love But they're never gonna see another one like I have with you",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 8.220000267028809,
      "text": "I see you lookin' good by the way you walk",
      "start": 0
    },
    {
      "end": 13,
      "text": "I see you lookin' so good, makes your light shine",
      "start": 8.300000190734863
    },
    {
      "end": 15.9399995803833,
      "text": "I've been givin' you a golden hue",
      "start": 13.520000457763672
    },
    {
      "end": 19.479999542236328,
      "text": "It won't take me long, girl",
      "start": 16.239999771118164
    },
    {
      "end": 23.940000534057617,
      "text": "Just have a little drink this year",
      "start": 19.81999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 26.959999084472656,
      "text": "Won't take me long, girl",
      "start": 23.940000534057617
    },
    {
      "end": 31.420000076293945,
      "text": "You can tell me yes or no quite quickly",
      "start": 26.959999084472656
    },
    {
      "end": 34.959999084472656,
      "text": "Has anybody ever told you you're",
      "start": 31.68000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 39.58000183105469,
      "text": "Like a magnet that makes me fall forward",
      "start": 35.599998474121094
    },
    {
      "end": 43.84000015258789,
      "text": "No matter if I wanna repeat past mistakes",
      "start": 39.79999923706055
    },
    {
      "end": 47.41999816894531,
      "text": "You're the thing that makes me do better",
      "start": 43.84000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 50.900001525878906,
      "text": "But it won't take me long",
      "start": 47.41999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 55.79999923706055,
      "text": "To tell you all the ways you help me know",
      "start": 51
    },
    {
      "end": 58.34000015258789,
      "text": "Won't take me long",
      "start": 55.79999923706055
    },
    {
      "end": 63.97999954223633,
      "text": "For me to show you just all the ways you could complete me",
      "start": 59.2400016784668
    },
    {
      "end": 69.44000244140625,
      "text": "But we can wait a little second left, not a little second right",
      "start": 64.19999694824219
    },
    {
      "end": 71.9800033569336,
      "text": "We're not here to fight, no",
      "start": 69.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 76.4000015258789,
      "text": "I know I just talked to you now we just met",
      "start": 72.31999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 79.94000244140625,
      "text": "But maybe you deserve a second round",
      "start": 76.4000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 84.36000061035156,
      "text": "It's not gonna take me long",
      "start": 80.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 88.05999755859375,
      "text": "With your heart singin' that song",
      "start": 84.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 92.4800033569336,
      "text": "It's not gonna take me long",
      "start": 88.05999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 95.55999755859375,
      "text": "When we're combustin' in the sheets",
      "start": 92.4800033569336
    },
    {
      "end": 104.77999877929688,
      "text": "Yeah, I feel so free, I'm flyin' now",
      "start": 96.37999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 108.36000061035156,
      "text": "Thank you for all the days when it",
      "start": 104.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 114.36000061035156,
      "text": "Oh, girl, it won't take me long",
      "start": 108.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 119.4000015258789,
      "text": "To imagine a future long with happiness",
      "start": 115.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 122.44000244140625,
      "text": "It won't take me long",
      "start": 119.4000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 127.9800033569336,
      "text": "Till you've got me inside of you",
      "start": 123.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 131.5800018310547,
      "text": "Like my love for kindness",
      "start": 129.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 135.5,
      "text": "Like my shining lining",
      "start": 133.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 139.4199981689453,
      "text": "Like the silver that binds us all together",
      "start": 135.5
    },
    {
      "end": 143.33999633789062,
      "text": "Gray matter from the heart is like a red tether",
      "start": 139.4199981689453
    },
    {
      "end": 147.17999267578125,
      "text": "And it's not gonna take me long",
      "start": 143.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 152.16000366210938,
      "text": "It's not gonna take me long at all",
      "start": 148
    },
    {
      "end": 159.4600067138672,
      "text": "To love you like you've never been in love before, baby",
      "start": 152.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 165.47999572753906,
      "text": "All this emotional stunt I'm runnin' to you",
      "start": 159.5
    },
    {
      "end": 169.33999633789062,
      "text": "Now I can see that we're right together",
      "start": 165.47999572753906
    },
    {
      "end": 172.0800018310547,
      "text": "Even if we just met, imagine that",
      "start": 169.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 175.83999633789062,
      "text": "Imagine all this in the span of this total second",
      "start": 172.0800018310547
    },
    {
      "end": 179.5,
      "text": "So just think of what a lover I could be",
      "start": 175.83999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 183.63999938964844,
      "text": "And just think about a better season",
      "start": 179.6199951171875
    },
    {
      "end": 186.74000549316406,
      "text": "You'll see that's the line",
      "start": 183.83999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 190.8000030517578,
      "text": "We're gonna pass dead right here all night",
      "start": 186.83999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 194.72000122070312,
      "text": "Oh, baby, it won't take me long",
      "start": 190.8000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 199.8800048828125,
      "text": "To love every second that I'm around you",
      "start": 195.8000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 202.5800018310547,
      "text": "It won't take me long",
      "start": 200.8000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 209.22000122070312,
      "text": "Cause you're dynamite and I'm so glad I met you",
      "start": 203.8000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 217.22000122070312,
      "text": "These eyes are cryin'",
      "start": 213.60000610351562
    },
    {
      "end": 219.3000030517578,
      "text": "These eyes have seen a lot of love",
      "start": 217.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 223.3000030517578,
      "text": "But they're never gonna see another one like I have with you",
      "start": 219.3000030517578
    }
